	   <tr><td colspan=2>Yes, all but three level 29 mage spells can be bought at merchants: these three spells are pets that must be researched.  All of the other spells can be bought, but the game makes this hard because different merchants sell different spells.<br><br>Most of your spells (Burnout II, Greater Summoning: Fire, Inferno Shield) can be purchased at most magician guilds in any city.<br><br>Two of your spells (Sword of Runes and Summon Coldstone) are only sold at special merchants, found in Ak`Anon, Erudin, and Neriak, in the spellcasters' guild.<br><br>The other three (Greater Summoning: Water, Air, and Earth) must be researched.<br><br>Hope this helps!<br><br>Rascarcapac, level 51 Elementalist, Xev Server.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
