	   <tr><td colspan=2>Cool, thanks for the info. Many things certaintly have changed since I played my magician.<br><br>Although, you can kill giants and spectors at level 34. In fact, spectors aren't that hard to kill becuase of their very low HP. The giants are much harder, making it so that you need to use the chain-summoning technique, which is why they are not efficient to kill until 39.<br><br>When I was talking about Unrest yard trash i was also referring to the first floor. Although these days Unrest sucks, so I should take that part out altogether anyway.<br><br>I will edit it a bit later when I get some more time, thanks!<br><br>P.S. - My guide was recently accepted to the Mage's Compedium site by the guy who built the site. I am not sure if he posted it yet becuase I said I still had to rewrite it a little, and never got back to him, but he probably put it up by now anyway.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
