	   <tr><td colspan=2>My standard Config is:<br>1) Summon spell (Pet, item, Summon Companion Etc)<br>2) Personal Buff<br>3) Gate/Expidience/Summon<br>4) Pet heal<br>5) Burnout<br>6) Bolt/Last circle nuke (or nuke of different type than in slot 8)<br>7) Damage shield<br>8) Primary nuke (Shock of Swords currently)<br><br>I try and keep a low mana nuke loaded for faster casting and lower costs. I also try and keep 2 "flavors" of nukes up... one Fire based, on magic based... for exploiting weaknesses<br> Unless I'm soloing I don't keep Phantom Armor loaded just because of the cost of the gems. (Phantom Plate takes 3 Catseyes. That is 10 castings out of 3 stacks, not much when you consider I camp for many long hours and am often away from gem vendors for weeks.)<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Thayn Bloodraven<br>Erudite Mage<br>Master Smith<br>Journeyman Tailor<br>Vazaelle</td></tr>
