<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=100716249916732></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f100716249916732><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=12&mid=100716249916732>RE: Spell gem management</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=12&mid=100716249916732#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=73372><span id= >Malaclypse</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>23 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Nov 30th 6:21 PM 2001</td>
