	   <tr><td colspan=2>The weapons are required from 24 up until the 39th lvl pets for duel wield but that is the only use for them.  They add no dammage or speed increase since the weapon del isn't counted when it comes to weapons for pets.  Once you get the 39th lvl pets the only thing the weapons will do for you is to make the pet look cool. The only exception to this is is if the weapon has a proc then the proc will work but no weapon dammage.<br><br>Cilditin 55th Mage (Povar)<br>Bedin 55th Shaman (Povar)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
